sequenceDiagram
    actor O as Operator
    participant B as Browser
    participant API as POST /api/payments
    participant V as Zod Validator
    participant DB as PostgreSQL
    participant Q as BullMQ (Redis)
    participant W as Notification Worker
    participant F as Fonnte API

    O->>B: Submit form pembayaran
    B->>API: POST { customerId, amount, periodMonth, method }
    API->>V: createPaymentSchema.parse()
    V-->>API: ok
    API->>DB: SELECT customer WHERE id=?
    DB-->>API: customer
    API->>API: generateInvoiceNumber()
    API->>DB: INSERT INTO payments (status='paid')
    DB-->>API: payment
    API->>Q: enqueueWhatsAppBilling({ phone, name, invoice, amount, periodMonth })
    API-->>B: 201 { payment }
    B-->>O: Tampilkan kuitansi digital

    Q->>W: deliver job WHATSAPP_BILLING
    W->>W: composeMessage() (B.Indonesia)
    W->>F: POST /send Authorization: Bearer FONNTE_TOKEN<br/>{ target: phone, message: text }
    F-->>W: 200 { detail: "ok" }
    W->>Q: ack
